text: The Man from Nowhere () is a 1961 Soviet comedy movie directed by Eldar Ryazanov.ЧЕЛОВЕК НИОТКУДА It stars Sergey Yursky, Yury Yakovlev, and Anatoliy Papanov. == Actors == * Sergey Yursky as Chudak * Yury Yakovlev as Vladimir Porazhayev * Anatoliy Papanov as Krokhalyov * Lyudmila Gurchenko as Lena * Anatoly Adoskin as Mikhail == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Russian comedy movies Category:1961 comedy movies Category:1961 science fiction movies Category:Movies directed by Eldar Ryazanov Category:Soviet comedy movies
title: The Man from Nowhere (1961 movie)
